   Politics &amp; Policy:
   Mexico Concerned Over Canadian Role
   In Talks With U.S. on Free-Trade Pact
   ----
   By Peter Truell
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
09/28/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A16
</SO>
